      <a href="/howto">신청방법</a>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/BHS5pw3">지원서버</a>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
    <% if (exists) { %>
      <h3>이런, 이미 등록한 서버가 있어요!</h3>
